Liverpool captain  Steven Gerrard 
will miss the rest of the season after a setback with his
injury, the Premier League soccer club said today on its
website.  The midfielder had surgery last month and reinjured himself
during training last week, manager  Kenny Dalglish  said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
